  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Sociology (Arts)              : Sociological examination of the human body as a cultural phenomenon that intersects with identity, health, illness, disability and medicine. Exploration of meanings attributed to human bodies as well as the body as a site of social interaction.          </p>

