      Sociology (Arts)              : A survey of theories of organization with particular reference to problems of growth, technology, centralization and decentralization, and organizational environments.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
